s of the colored regions are conic sections. Not shown is the other half of=
 the hyperbola, which is on the unshown other half of the double cone.</fig=
caption></figure>
<figure class=3D"mw-default-size" typeof=3D"mw:File/Thumb"><a href=3D"https=
