-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.671ex; width:1.332ex; height:2.509ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle \be=
ta }"></span> and the angle between the cutting plane and the axis is <span=
 class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math=
-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=
