<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Discriminant">Discriminant<=
/h4></div>
<p>The conic sections described by this equation can be classified in terms=
 of the value <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><spa=
n class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: n=
one;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displ=
aystyle B^{2}-4AC}">
