{2}+1=3D0,}"></span> or to an <i>imaginary ellipse</i>, such as with the eq=
uation <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class=
=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none;"><=
