 href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Poisson_distribution" title=3D"Poiss=
on distribution">Poisson distributions</a> as parabolic, and <a href=3D"htt=
ps://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negative_binomial_distribution" title=3D"Negativ=
e binomial distribution">negative binomial distributions</a> as hyperbolic.=
 This is elaborated at <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cumulant#Cu=
mulants_of_some_discrete_probability_distributions" title=3D"Cumulant">cumu=
lants of some discrete probability distributions</a>.</dd></dl>
